hmp3 : an ncurses mp3 frontend written in Haskell

Dependencies:
        The mpg321 program

Building:
        $ autoreconf
        $ runhaskell Setup.lhs configure --prefix=/home/dons
        $ runhaskell Setup.lhs build
        $ runhaskell Setup.lhs install

License:
        GPL

Author:
        Don Stewart, Thu Nov 10 16:26:23 EST 2005
